<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <%- include('partials/head'); %>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/dashboard.css?v=20260405-3" type="text/css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/landing.css?v=20260405-1" type="text/css">
</head>
<body class="body-container">

<header>
  <%- include('partials/header', { navItem: 'landing' }); %>
</header>

<main class="landing-main">
  <section class="landing-hero">
    <div class="landing-copy">
      <div class="landing-kicker">Waiting for a price drop? </div>
      <h1>Get notified as soon as the price drops!</h1>
      <p class="landing-lede">
        Pricewatcher keeps an eye on the products you care about and gives you one clean place to see what moved up, what dropped, and what is worth buying now.
      </p>
      <div class="landing-actions">
        <a class="btn landing-primary-action" href="/auth/signup">Create account</a>
        <a class="btn landing-secondary-action" href="/auth/login">Log in</a>
      </div>
      <div class="landing-mobile-preview">
        <img
          class="landing-mobile-preview-image"
          src="/images/example-my-tracks-list.png"
          alt="Example of the My tracks list"
        >
      </div>
      <p class="landing-footnote">
        Sign up or log in to start tracking prices!
      </p>

      <div class="landing-feature-grid">
        <article class="landing-feature-card">
          <h2>One watchlist</h2>
          <p>Keep all your tracked products in a single place instead of scattering bookmarks across shops.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="landing-feature-card">
          <h2>Clear price movement</h2>
          <p>Get an email notification when a price change occurs to make sure you don't miss a good deal.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="landing-feature-card">
          <h2>Fewer missed deals</h2>
          <p>Let the service do the repetitive checking so you only pay attention when something actually changes.</p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="landing-visual">
      <div class="dashboard-window dashboard-window-demo">
        <div class="dashboard-toolbar">
          <span class="dashboard-toolbar-dot dashboard-toolbar-dot-red"></span>
          <span class="dashboard-toolbar-dot dashboard-toolbar-dot-amber"></span>
          <span class="dashboard-toolbar-dot dashboard-toolbar-dot-green"></span>
          <div class="dashboard-toolbar-url">pricewatcher.birgirs.com/my-tracks</div>
        </div>
        <div class="dashboard-content">
          <div class="dashboard-header">
            <div>
              <p class="dashboard-label">Example dashboard</p>
              <h2>My tracked products</h2>
              <p class="dashboard-subtitle">The real dashboard uses the same structure, with expandable rows for link and price history details.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="dashboard-summary">
              <strong>4</strong>
              <span>active tracks</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="dashboard-table-wrap">
            <table class="dashboard-table" aria-label="Example tracked products">
              <thead>
                <tr>
                  <th>Product</th>
                  <th>Original</th>
                  <th>Current</th>
                  <th>Status</th>
                </tr>
              </thead>
              <tbody>
                <tr>
                  <td data-label="Product">
                    <span class="dashboard-product-name">Nintendo Switch OLED</span>
                    <span class="dashboard-product-meta">elko.is &middot; Added Jan 12, 2026</span>
                  </td>
                  <td class="dashboard-number-cell" data-label="Original">54,990</td>
                  <td class="dashboard-number-cell" data-label="Current">
                    <span class="dashboard-price-pill dashboard-price-drop">49,990</span>
                  </td>
                  <td data-label="Status">
                    <span class="dashboard-status-pill dashboard-status-drop">Dropped</span>
                  </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td data-label="Product">
                    <span class="dashboard-product-name">Sony WH-1000XM5</span>
                    <span class="dashboard-product-meta">ht.is &middot; Added Feb 4, 2026</span>
                  </td>
                  <td class="dashboard-number-cell" data-label="Original">59,999</td>
                  <td class="dashboard-number-cell" data-label="Current">
                    <span class="dashboard-price-pill dashboard-price-drop">52,490</span>
                  </td>
                  <td data-label="Status">
                    <span class="dashboard-status-pill dashboard-status-drop">Dropped</span>
                  </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td data-label="Product">
                    <span class="dashboard-product-name">Dyson V15 Detect</span>
                    <span class="dashboard-product-meta">rafha.is &middot; Added Mar 9, 2026</span>
                  </td>
                  <td class="dashboard-number-cell" data-label="Original">119,990</td>
                  <td class="dashboard-number-cell" data-label="Current">
                    <span class="dashboard-price-pill dashboard-price-flat">119,990</span>
                  </td>
                  <td data-label="Status">
                    <span class="dashboard-status-pill dashboard-status-flat">Steady</span>
                  </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td data-label="Product">
                    <span class="dashboard-product-name">Apple Watch Series 10</span>
                    <span class="dashboard-product-meta">tl.is &middot; Added Mar 14, 2026</span>
                  </td>
                  <td class="dashboard-number-cell" data-label="Original">74,990</td>
                  <td class="dashboard-number-cell" data-label="Current">
                    <span class="dashboard-price-pill dashboard-price-rise">79,990</span>
                  </td>
                  <td data-label="Status">
                    <span class="dashboard-status-pill dashboard-status-rise">Higher</span>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>

          <div class="dashboard-note">
            <strong>What you get:</strong> a quick read on whether it is finally time to buy, wait, or keep watching.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>

<footer>
  <%- include('partials/footer'); %>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
